{"tid":2129484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾庭耀：為保障票站調查員的人生安全 9月選舉暫停所有票站調查 並不會做任何配票工作","createTime":"2020-07-28T15:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T15:21:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"744335ba7f5dc906c1dc226fd86757b96bbe21fe","tid":2129484,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:20:36.000Z","msg":"鍾庭耀重申，有關決定和《國安法》無關，但由於社會分化、以及在新法律框架下有難以預測的風險，基於對學生人身安全的考慮，決定煞停票站調查，「唔好連累佢哋」。鍾續指，社會目前仍未了解《國安法》的實際操作，故民研的態度暫時「當佢冇到先」，但重申仍要非常小心，避免其團隊受到外界滋擾，「唔知有冇人會有搜查令，又上嚟搞一搞」。<br />\n<br />\n立法會選舉將於9月6日舉行，政界盛傳港府極有可能將選舉押後。鍾庭耀指，目前假設選舉會如期舉行，如選舉提名期於月底完成，將展開與民主動力合作的滾動調查，但表明會因應情況作重新調整。鍾稱，如選舉延期逾一年，計劃將即時停止，惟目前押後與否仍然未明，表示「最唔想見到一切都唔清唔楚」。<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀強調，民研不會參與任何組織選舉配票工作，但預期會有組識按數據進行配票，引致最終結果與滾動調查數據有落差<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200728/NW2IL7LSKA5U46PE6EQMQX2X3U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200728%2FNW2IL7LSKA5U46PE6EQMQX2X3U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD9HbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=c85074b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200728%2FNW2IL7LSKA5U46PE6EQMQX2X3U%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=a128fcac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200728/NW2IL7LSKA5U46PE6EQMQX2X3U/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"e8003e4cab3bb0c815391b05230a2e45cb097e14","tid":2129484,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T15:21:43.000Z","msg":"選都冇撚得選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}